'''尼古拉公司'''（Nikola Corporation）是[[美国|美国]]的一家零排放[[汽车|汽车]]生产商，總部位于[[亞利桑那州|亞利桑那州]][[鳳凰城|鳳凰城]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bizjournals.com/phoenix/news/2018/10/19/behind-the-deal-how-nikola-motor-steered-its.html|title=Behind the deal: How Nikola Motor steered its trucking technology to Arizona|last=Ringle|first=Hayley|date=2018-10-19|website=Phoenix Business Journal|access-date=2019-01-07|archive-date=2020-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819021928/https://www.bizjournals.com/phoenix/news/2018/10/19/behind-the-deal-how-nikola-motor-steered-its.html}}</ref>。公司以[[尼古拉·特斯拉|尼古拉·特斯拉]]的名字命名<ref>{{cite news |last=Cao |first=Sissi |date=2019-11-23 |title=Elon Musk Isn’t the Only Electric Futurist Who Wants to Rectify Nikola Tesla’s Legacy |url=https://observer.com/2019/11/elon-musk-tesla-electric-vehicle-rival-nikola-hydrogen-truck/ |website=Observer |access-date=2020-06-12 |archive-date=2020-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200612090703/https://observer.com/2019/11/elon-musk-tesla-electric-vehicle-rival-nikola-hydrogen-truck/ }}</ref>。尼古拉公司于2014年在[[犹他州|犹他州]][[鹽湖城|鹽湖城]]成立<ref>{{cite news|last=Hsu|first=Tiffany|date=2016-12-01|title=Nikola One Hydrogen Fuel Cell Electric Semi-Truck Debuts|website=Trucks.com|url=https://www.trucks.com/2016/12/01/nikola-one-hydrogen-fuel-cell-electric-semi-truck-debuts|access-date=2020-06-12|archive-date=2016-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161203142547/https://www.trucks.com/2016/12/01/nikola-one-hydrogen-fuel-cell-electric-semi-truck-debuts/}}</ref>，创办人暨執行主席為[[特雷弗·米尔顿|特雷弗·米尔顿]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/profile/trevor-milton/#54dcf1ff8861|title=Forbes profile: Trevor Milton|work=Forbes|access-date=2020-07-27|archive-date=2020-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200727072517/https://www.forbes.com/profile/trevor-milton/#54dcf1ff8861}}</ref>。

==爭議==
做空機構{{tsl|en|Hindenburg Research|Hindenburg Research}}曾在2020年9月10日發布報告指出，尼古拉聯合創始人兼執行長米爾頓，涉嫌誇大該公司電動卡車測試結果，和測試影片內容詐欺。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/nikola-internal-review-confirms-some-claims-in-short-sellers-report-11614350745 |title=Nikola Internal Review Confirms Some Claims in Short Seller’s Report |last=Foldy |first=Ben |date=2021-02-26 |newspaper=Wall Street Journal |accessdate=2022-02-20 |language=en-US |issn=0099-9660 |archive-date=2022-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220220070054/https://www.wsj.com/articles/nikola-internal-review-confirms-some-claims-in-short-sellers-report-11614350745 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

隨後尼古拉公司股市大跌，创办人[[特雷弗·米尔顿|特雷弗·米尔顿]]因此宣布請辭董事會。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://ec.ltn.com.tw/amp/article/breakingnews/3298541 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-10-16 |archive-date=2020-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924075524/https://ec.ltn.com.tw/amp/article/breakingnews/3298541 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

